  "section_name": "Financial Analysis",
  "text": "Profitability metrics reflect strong net margin performance, with Q3 2025 net margin at 27.86%, up from 25.80% in Q3 2024. The margin expansion trend continued through 2025, with Q1 2025 at 26.84% and Q2 2025 at 27.95%, indicating consistent profitability improvement. Net income grew to $2,902,000,000 in Q3 2025 from $2,507,000,000 in Q3 2024. However, gross margin and operating margin data are not available in the provided financial statements, limiting comprehensive margin analysis.",
